6
00:00:46,800 --> 00:00:51,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Eommoni (Ibu), ini obat herbal yang kita cari.</font>

7
00:01:03,600 --> 00:01:06,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Pasti segera membaik sesaat setelah mengonsumsinya.</font>

8
00:01:11,600 --> 00:01:13,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayo!</font>

9
00:01:17,900 --> 00:01:20,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau hampir dapat masalah besar!</font>

10
00:01:23,600 --> 00:01:26,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi, kau baik-baik saja?</font>

11
00:01:29,200 --> 00:01:31,590
<font color=#FFFF00>A... apa kau terluka?</font>

12
00:01:53,600 --> 00:01:55,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku...</font>

13
00:01:57,100 --> 00:01:59,300
<font color=#FFFF00>...tampan tidak?</font>

14
00:02:00,700 --> 00:02:02,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

15
00:02:02,090 --> 00:02:09,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau... satu-satunya orang yang melihat wajahku setelah sekian lama.</font>

16
00:02:13,700 --> 00:02:17,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimanapun, terima kasih bantuannya.</font>

17
00:02:17,100 --> 00:02:18,900
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku selamat berkat dirimu.</font>

18
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:28,080
<font color=#FFFF00><i>[Jongmyo]</i></font>

19
00:02:29,200 --> 00:02:31,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Ritualnya dipersiapkan secara menyeluruh oleh Jongmyo.</font>

20
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:33,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Sun-Gun (Pangeran Yi Sun)?</font>

21
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:35,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Hamba yakin beliau kabur jauh sebelum persiapan dimulai.</font>

22
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:38,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa juga dia melarikan diri?
Dia tidak punya tempat tujuan.</font>

23
00:02:38,690 --> 00:02:42,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Pyunsoo-hwe (Kelompok Pyunsoo) dapat menangkapnya,
lalu...</font>

24
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:44,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Hamba akan segera menemukan Jeoha (Yang Mulia).</font>

25
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:48,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak, jangan membuat pergerakan mencurigakan.</font>

26
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:51,500
<font color=#FFFF00>Pyeonsoo-hwe pasti mengawasi pergerakanmu.</font>

27
00:02:51,500 --> 00:02:54,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Silakan melangkah, Cheonha (Yang Mulia).</font>

28
00:02:57,590 --> 00:02:59,900
<font color=#FFFF00>Chung Woon dimana sekarang?</font>

29
00:03:00,500 --> 00:03:02,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Cheonha...</font>

30
00:03:02,090 --> 00:03:05,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Putera hamba telah bekerja
dengan hamba begitu lama, namun...</font>

31
00:03:05,090 --> 00:03:07,400
<font color=#FFFF00>...Chung Woon tidak tahu perihal wajah Seja (Putera Mahkota).</font>

32
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:09,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau begitu, ia tidak bisa membantu.</font>

33
00:03:09,590 --> 00:03:11,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Cepat bawa Chung Woon secepatnya.</font>

34
00:03:11,590 --> 00:03:12,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Baik.</font>

35
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:26,000
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Sunjo (salah seorang Raja Joseon), aku mendoakanmu.</i></font>

36
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:28,400
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kau tidak bijaksana,</i></font>

37
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:31,000
<font color=#FFFF00><i>sampai menelantarkan rakyatmu sendiri,</i></font>

38
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:34,190
<font color=#FFFF00><i>kau telah menjadi Raja lalim yang tak menghiraukan
kehendak langit.</i></font>

39
00:03:34,190 --> 00:03:37,590
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Namun, Seja berbeda.</i></font>

40
00:03:37,590 --> 00:03:41,400
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Dia satu-satunya harapan bagi Joseon
untuk kembali kokoh.</i></font>

41
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:47,000
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Tolong, lindungilah anak itu, Sunjo.</i></font>

42
00:03:47,020 --> 00:03:52,020
<font color=#FFFF00>Penerjemah .: Writer Ayra :.</font>

43
00:04:00,500 --> 00:04:03,900
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku... hanya pergi ke arah yang sama.</font>

44
00:04:07,900 --> 00:04:10,900
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi, kau juga ke Seosomun?</font>

45
00:04:11,500 --> 00:04:14,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau terus bicara informal padaku?</font>

46
00:04:15,590 --> 00:04:18,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, asal kau tahu.</font>

47
00:04:18,890 --> 00:04:22,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku... sebenarnya orang yang berhak bicara informal padamu.</font>

48
00:04:22,190 --> 00:04:23,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

49
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:25,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Aih, memang siapa dirimu?</font>

50
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:28,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku? Aku...</font>

51
00:04:33,690 --> 00:04:35,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku...</font>

52
00:04:35,890 --> 00:04:37,600
<font color=#FFFF00>...anggota organisasi literasi.</font>

53
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:38,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Literasi?</font>

54
00:04:38,890 --> 00:04:42,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Auh, kalau begitu kau pasti mengetahui banyak buku langka seumur hidupmu.</font>

55
00:04:42,390 --> 00:04:45,600
<font color=#FFFF00>"Survey of Roads" atau "Survey of Mountains and Rivers",
tahu judul itu?</font>

56
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:47,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana dengan...
"Unabridged Compilation of Herbal Lore?"</font>

57
00:04:47,890 --> 00:04:51,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Aih... kau membaca semua buku itu?</font>

58
00:04:51,390 --> 00:04:52,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak.</font>

59
00:04:52,690 --> 00:04:55,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sangat ingin membacanya,
tapi sampai sekarang belum mendapatkan bukunya.</font>

60
00:04:55,800 --> 00:05:00,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau bisa mendapatkan buku-buku pengobatan
atau ajaran barat?</font>

61
00:05:00,300 --> 00:05:04,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Ah, sebenarnya aku punya buku terjemahan ajaran barat di sini.</font>

62
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:07,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini.</font>

63
00:05:08,500 --> 00:05:10,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga!</font>

64
00:05:10,300 --> 00:05:12,390
<font color=#FFFF00>"The Chronicles of Foreign Lands"!</font>

65
00:05:12,390 --> 00:05:16,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Ah, tapi darimana kau mendapatkan buku berharga ini?</font>

66
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:21,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Aih, andai kau tahu siapa aku sebenarnya!</font>

67
00:05:21,390 --> 00:05:25,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku... seseorang yang mampu mendapatkan
buku-buku semacam ini dengan mudah.</font>

68
00:05:26,890 --> 00:05:30,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, sayang sekali.
Bukunya kan berharga sekali.</font>

69
00:05:35,100 --> 00:05:36,500
<font color=#FFFF00>Aih... bagaimana bisa!?</font>

70
00:05:36,500 --> 00:05:39,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Aih, padahal mau kuberikan pada Woo Bo!</font>

71
00:05:39,690 --> 00:05:41,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Profesor Woo Bo?</font>

72
00:05:42,500 --> 00:05:45,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau... mengenal Woo Bo?</font>

73
00:05:45,390 --> 00:05:47,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, dia guruku.</font>

74
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:50,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Sebenarnya aku sedang akan menemui beliau.</font>

75
00:05:50,600 --> 00:05:51,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Begitukah?</font>

76
00:05:53,190 --> 00:05:54,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi, kau...</font>

77
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:59,890
<font color=#FFFF00>...murid Woo Bo penggila buku geografi, agama, dan pengobatan itu?</font>

78
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:03,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Namamu siapa?</font>

79
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:06,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Lalu, kau sendiri?</font>

80
00:06:06,690 --> 00:06:08,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku...</font>

81
00:06:10,600 --> 00:06:12,600
<font color=#FFFF00>...Chun Soo.</font>

82
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:16,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku Ga Eun,
Han Ga Eun.</font>

83
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:19,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Tolong tunggu di sini sebentar.</font>

84
00:06:19,390 --> 00:06:23,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Tunggu, kenapa?
Aku tidak boleh ikut bersamamu?</font>

85
00:06:23,190 --> 00:06:25,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan segera kembali.</font>

86
00:06:29,870 --> 00:06:32,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Diamlah dulu. Apa saja yang sudah kau lakukan?</font>

87
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:33,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Auh...</font>

88
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:35,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Lee Sun-ah, kau tak apa?</font>

89
00:06:35,390 --> 00:06:36,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Aghassi (Nona)!</font>

90
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:38,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Terjadi keributan besar lagi di tengah kota hari ini.</font>

91
00:06:38,890 --> 00:06:40,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku baik-baik saja, Nona.</font>

92
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:42,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Assi (Nona)...</font>

93
00:06:42,190 --> 00:06:45,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Tolong mampir sebentar nanti.</font>

94
00:06:45,190 --> 00:06:48,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada yang ingin saya berikan meski tidak banyak.</font>

95
00:06:48,100 --> 00:06:51,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Bibi kan tidak bekerja untuk keluarga kami,
tapi selalu memperhatikan kami.</font>

96
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:52,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Maafkan aku.</font>

97
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:55,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Auh, kenapa mengatakan hal semacam itu?</font>

98
00:06:55,690 --> 00:06:59,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Tuan Seo Yoon (Ayah Ga Eun),
sudah sangat baik pada kami.</font>

99
00:06:59,190 --> 00:07:00,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Aih, Assi ada di sini?</font>

100
00:07:00,890 --> 00:07:02,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Halo.</font>

101
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:08,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukankah sudah kularang kau membuat masalah?</font>

102
00:07:08,890 --> 00:07:10,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa memukulku?</font>

103
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:13,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Sudah kubilang tangkap pencurinya.
Kenapa malah membuat keributan?</font>

104
00:07:13,690 --> 00:07:15,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tahu kesulitan apa yang kulalui karenamu, Nak?</font>

105
00:07:15,190 --> 00:07:17,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka yang memukuli aku.</font>

106
00:07:17,390 --> 00:07:21,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Ish... kenapa juga kau terima dipukuli olehnya seperti idiot?
Kenapa?</font>

107
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:23,750
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sudah cukup membuat masalah dengan ingin belajar membaca.</font>

108
00:07:23,750 --> 00:07:27,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Memang ada untungnya kalau kau bisa membaca!?</font>

109
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:31,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau... sungguh tidak terluka?</font>

110
00:07:34,500 --> 00:07:38,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu bukan hal mustahil. Lee Sun sangat cerdas.</font>

111
00:07:38,690 --> 00:07:41,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia bisa mengingat segalanya dengan sekali lihat
(memori fotografis?),</font>

112
00:07:41,190 --> 00:07:43,000
<font color=#FFFF00>bahkan Profesor memujinya jenius.</font>

113
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:45,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Aigoo... Assi berlebihan.</font>

114
00:07:45,890 --> 00:07:48,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak ada untungnya meski dia jenius.</font>

115
00:07:56,100 --> 00:08:01,500
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak bisa makan karena sibuk.</font>

116
00:08:03,690 --> 00:08:07,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, kau!
Kita ini dimana?</font>

117
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:09,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku... juga tidak tahu.</font>

118
00:08:14,190 --> 00:08:15,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Ah!</font>

119
00:08:15,190 --> 00:08:18,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau ada di sini,
tapi bahkan tidak tahu dimana tepatnya?</font>

120
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:20,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau memukulku?</font>

121
00:08:26,100 --> 00:08:28,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Lalu ingin aku bagaimana?</font>

122
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:40,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau menghabiskan alkoholku?</font>

123
00:08:40,100 --> 00:08:44,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa? Kau yang memberikan botol kosong padaku!</font>

124
00:08:48,790 --> 00:08:51,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Masih sisa sedikit.</font>

125
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:04,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi...</font>

126
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:07,290
<font color=#FFFF00>...kita dimana?</font>

127
00:09:08,700 --> 00:09:12,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Dimana kita? Dimana?</font>

128
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:13,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Aish!</font>

129
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:17,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Ow!</font>

130
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:19,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana bisa kau di sini?</font>

131
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:22,700
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sendiri? Kenapa lama sekali?</font>

132
00:09:22,700 --> 00:09:24,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Orang gila--</font>

133
00:09:25,100 --> 00:09:26,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh?</font>

134
00:09:27,100 --> 00:09:30,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau... pemuda di sana tadi?</font>

135
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:38,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Apakah sungguh tidak masalah membawa dia pada
Profesor Woo Bo?</font>

136
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:40,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau... juga anak didiknya?</font>

137
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:43,700
<font color=#FFFF00>Ikuti aku.</font>

138
00:09:54,600 --> 00:09:57,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Sebentar. Sebentar. Sebentar.</font>

139
00:09:57,000 --> 00:10:03,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini... sungguh kediaman Profesor Woo Bo?</font>

140
00:10:10,390 --> 00:10:11,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada apa?</font>

141
00:10:11,390 --> 00:10:12,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Profesor!</font>

142
00:10:15,100 --> 00:10:16,790
<font color=#FFFF00>- Wow.
- Profesor?</font>

143
00:10:21,600 --> 00:10:23,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Profesor.</font>

144
00:10:29,500 --> 00:10:33,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku yakin kau membawaku ke tempat yang salah.</font>

145
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:34,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

146
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:36,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Pria yang kucari adalah sarjana hebat, Woo Bo.</font>

147
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:38,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, ini Profesor Woo Bo.</font>

148
00:10:38,600 --> 00:10:39,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukan!</font>

149
00:10:39,600 --> 00:10:42,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukan pria tua pemabuk ini.
Woo Bo!</font>

150
00:10:42,390 --> 00:10:45,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Sarjana hebat, Woo Bo,
dahulu seorang Profesor Sungkyunkwan.</font>

151
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:52,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Profesor.</font>

152
00:10:52,290 --> 00:10:55,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Um... um... ya?</font>

153
00:10:55,390 --> 00:10:57,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Dimana aku?</font>

154
00:10:57,200 --> 00:11:00,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Pria ini anggota kelompok literasi
yang ingin memberi Profesor buku,</font>

155
00:11:00,390 --> 00:11:01,890
<font color=#FFFF00>makanya saya bawa kemari.</font>

156
00:11:02,890 --> 00:11:04,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Literasi?</font>

157
00:11:04,390 --> 00:11:07,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Yeonggam (Pak Tua), kau sungguh Profesor Woo Bo?</font>

158
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:10,700
<font color=#FFFF00>Woo Bo.
Aku memang Woo Bo.</font>

159
00:11:10,700 --> 00:11:13,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi, aku bukan Profesor.</font>

160
00:11:22,600 --> 00:11:25,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Lihat. Ini "The Chronicles of Foreign Lands."</font>

161
00:11:25,600 --> 00:11:28,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Buku ini hanya ada satu di Joseon.</font>

162
00:11:29,700 --> 00:11:33,700
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kau bisa menjawab pertanyaanku,
maka akan kuberikan buku ini.</font>

163
00:11:38,700 --> 00:11:40,500
<font color=#FFFF00>Maafkan saya, Profesor.</font>

164
00:11:40,500 --> 00:11:42,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Saya tahu dia orang aneh, tapi...</font>

165
00:11:42,890 --> 00:11:45,390
<font color=#FFFF00>- Aduh!
- Saya tidak menyangka dia separah ini.</font>

166
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:55,700
<font color=#FFFF00>Tak apa. Kalian berdua keluar saja dulu.</font>

167
00:11:55,700 --> 00:11:57,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

168
00:11:58,890 --> 00:12:00,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Baik.</font>

169
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:04,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tahu siapa aku?</font>

170
00:12:04,890 --> 00:12:08,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Mana mungkin aku tahu saat kau bahkan
tidak memperkenalkan diri?</font>

171
00:12:09,500 --> 00:12:11,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Itukah pertanyaanmu untukku?</font>

172
00:12:14,790 --> 00:12:17,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah, aku akan menanyakannya.</font>

173
00:12:17,790 --> 00:12:21,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Seja harus memakai topeng,
apakah kau tahu alasan dibaliknya?</font>

174
00:12:21,600 --> 00:12:22,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tahu.</font>

175
00:12:23,890 --> 00:12:28,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Biar kutanya juga padamu.
Kau tahu soal Pyunsoo-hwe?</font>

176
00:12:28,890 --> 00:12:31,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Pyeonsoo-hwe?</font>

177
00:12:34,790 --> 00:12:39,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Aih, aku yang mestinya bertanya,
kenapa kau justru balik mengajukan pertanyaan padaku?</font>

178
00:12:39,200 --> 00:12:44,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sungguh mengetahui alasan Seja memakai topeng?</font>

179
00:12:44,100 --> 00:12:47,200
